body_html:
Lemme clarify the question a little bit.

We took the tutorial code for logistic regression for MNIST from the tensorflow website.

We used the same MNIST dataset from the tensorflow repository and used an equivalent logistic regression model in Theano.

We're not sure where the four-time timing difference comes from, although I suspect it's from the feed_dict and placeholder feature.

I don't see any documentation for the StepStats and timeline function. So I don't know how to use those to do profiling.

Can you please provide more instruction as to how to profile?

Thank you.
